value: ***Identifies variation in department size amongst HISD High schools***

***NOTE THAT 2003-04 IS MISSING YEAR-LONG COURSES****
***FIRST - SCHOOL-WIDE DEPARTMENTS***
**LIMIT TO HIGH SCHOOL ASPIRE GRADES & MIDDLE SCHOOL***
